		<h3>Info on Slashcode</h3>
		<p>Slashcode is the code for All Things Slash. Slash is the source code and database that was originally used to create <a href="http://slashdot.org/" target="blank">Slashdot</a>, and has now been released under the GNU General Public License. It is a bona fide Open Source / Free Software project.</p>
		<p>Good open source projects, depend on the community. Thanks for your continued support, and let us know what we can do to make the site better.</p>
		<p>Slash and Slashcode could not be possible without the use of some great Open Source software.</p>
